title: Frank Zappa - Hot Rats 1969 / 2008 Remaster / 2012
description:
Hot Rats is often considered as Frank Zappa's masterpiece; perfectly melding jazz and rock, giving his own vision of fusion. It remains a true masterpiece from one of the greatest geniuses of modern music.



Frank Zappa

 Hot Rats

 1969

 2012 reissue based on the 2008 remaster from the original 1969 analog master

 

 CD / 2012 / 320Kbps



 Tracklist:

 2. Willie The Pimp

 3. Son Of Mr. Green Genes

 4. Little Umbrellas

 5. The Gumbo Variations

 6. It Must Be A Camel
